<HL>
   Some Suppliers
   Refusing to Ship
   To Ames Stores
   ---
   Delays in Arrival of Goods
   For Spring May Worsen
   Chain's Financial Woes
   ----
   By Joseph Pereira
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
04/12/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A3
</SO>
